values:
I got really depressed about the 'break' with me & Seth the day before yesterday; & I binged HORRIBLY.  

I ate CHINESE FOOD.  I felt sooo disgusting...but I've doen fairly well today & yesterday; & I walked a bunch to make up for it.

I ate:

8 kernels of popcorn: 75 cals (?)
2 bites of pizza crust: 50 cals (?)

TOTAL: 125 cals.  I'm not EVEN going to add up the chinese food.  It would just depress me more. :(

I excercised:

walked 3 1/2 miles
20 crunches

Ok; I suppose...but I really need to fast to make up for my binge-fest.

Fuck. Fuck. Fuck.  Seth did it to me again.  So now I have to go to Cleveland BY MYSELF; same for BR -- & he's all "I'm staying here for 5 months.  Do waht you want."

Has he ever given a shit at all?

Eaten:

3 bites of pizza: 54 cals
1 bite of chocolate: 25 cals

Total: 79 cals

Excercise:

50 crunches
25 jjs

I hate myself & want to die.

Hum.  So Seth's not here & that makes me hungry.  I feel as though I might make-over my other journal -- it's starting to get a little stale.  I'm really tempted to add Lani or something...it's not like we don't have enough in common.  I want to find some secret fool-proof way to contact ehr & suggest the ana-buddy thing without it back-firign on me...grr.

I'm lonely & that makes me want to eat.  I'll go smoke a cigarette.

So this is going to be used purely as ana journal...because I really don't need any more shit from my friends.  

STATS:

CW: 89
HW: 116
GW: 80
5'0
BMI: 17.4

Officially ana BMI.  Whoo!  Today I ate:

2 bagels: 200 cals.

Nasties; but ok.  Fasting starts tomorrow.
